# Omarchy Cheatsheet

## Window Management
Super + Return          Terminal
Super + Space           App launcher
Super + Alt + Space     Omarchy menu
Super + Q               Close window
Super + F               Fullscreen
Super + V               Float toggle

## Workspaces (F-keys)
F1-F12                  Switch workspace
Alt + F1-F12            Move window to workspace*
Ctrl + F1-F12           Launch workspace
Super + grave           Utility workspace
*Alt+F9 broken by Framework EC - use Super+Shift+9

## Workspaces (number keys)
Super + Alt + 1-0,-,=   Switch to workspace 1-12
Super + Shift + 1-0,-,= Move window to workspace 1-12

## Navigation (vim-style)
Super + H/J/K/L         Focus left/down/up/right
Super + Shift + H/J/K/L Swap window (if window exists in that direction)
Super + Shift + ,/.     Resize width
Super + Shift + [/]     Resize height
Alt + J                 Toggle split (horizontal ↔ vertical)
Super + Shift + D       Toggle layout (dwindle ↔ master)
Fn + Left/Right         Beginning/end of line

## Screenshots
Super + Ctrl + 2        Full screen
Super + Ctrl + 3        Selection

## Apps
Super + Shift + T       Terminal
Super + Shift + B       Browser
Super + Shift + N       Editor
Super + Shift + F       File manager
Super + Shift + S       Music (Spotify)
Super + Shift + M       Activity (btop)
Super + Shift + A       ChatGPT
Super + Shift + E       Email
Super + Shift + /       1Password

## Audio
Super + Ctrl + A        Switch audio output

## Secrets & Config
vault-edit              Edit Ansible vault
secrets-pull            Pull & decrypt from B2
secrets-push            Encrypt & push to B2
om-secrets              Deploy secrets to system
om                      Run full Ansible playbook
om-config               Sync dotfiles only

## Other
Alt + K                 Show all hotkeys
Super + Alt + H         This cheatsheet
Super + Alt + J         Agenda (3 days)
